entries.femaleVariant: Hey! Where are you going? Get back here!
It's here. Come with me.
An abandoned construction site?
Goddamn city... Gave it all, then took it all right back...
Apparently, they lured her here. She didn't realize her life was in danger until was too late.
As good a place as any other. More importantly, away from others.
Where we headed?
Do it.
To the place they ended her life.
I want to see what she saw before I die.
Goodbye, Ken. You deserve this.
Goodbye, Ken.
Want to leave me no way out, is that it?
You sure?
Poetic.
Not exactly, it's just... it's how it ought to be.
At least she wasn't scared.
Yes. You're right...
Ken, listen... My company spat me out too. Was handed a dirty job by a higher-up. Thought it was game over for me.
You deserve this.
Sure about this?
I know.
Just do it.
Goodbye, Ken.
But I got help. He showed me it's possible to find meaning another way. Then I lost him too, just like you lost Enid.
There's the problem. I don't want it.
Fuck you! You hear me?!
I...I can do this... Just once...
But look at me! I got my life back! Stupid as it might sound, all you gotta do is want it back.
We had a deal, you hear me!? You gave your word!
And the platypuses?
W-what...? What platypuses?
The ones your daughter wanted to give life to. Her unfulfilled dream.
Why mention that? Do you want to see me drown in my grief even more?
Enid would consider you a coward.
You can fulfill her dream.
You're a coward, the pathetic way you just roll over.
If you die, the last memory of her dies with you, d'you understand? Like she never existed. You want that?
I lost everything. Where would even begin to get the resources for...for a biotech breakthrough?
It's true. Do you want my apology for being weak? Well, it's my right.
Do you think Enid would want this? That because--
Enid doesn't want anything! She can't because of me! You get that yet?! Just let me die!
What about the platypuses?
And if that person doesn't have the strength to live in a world without you?
I don't know.
It's not about the platypuses.
No clue – think of something. Make an effort. You're a hundred times smarter than me.
Maybe the platypuses are stupid idea – I dunno, you're the scientist. That's not what this is about.
I do know one thing. Life's a fucking roller coaster. I'm 24 and I... well, I could die really damn soon.
W-what? What're you talking about?
And y'know what? I don't want the world to forget about me. That's why I crawled out from the bottom through all the shit. Understand?
If there's anyone anywhere who cares about me, they better buckle their ass in and spend whatever time they can with me.
Then, when I'm dead, stand over my grave and rock their grandkids' minds with stories about how V lived for somethin'!
Then they better find it. For my sake.
Good luck, Ken.
